data.message: Yes we need awesome men to counsel!!!
Liking this just for "crutons". But I'm interested! I'm not yet sure if I'm free then, is there a deadline for signing up/applying?
The sooner the better but yeah there isnt a deadline. We are just worried about having to turn away boy campers who are signing up and we arent sure if there are enough counselors!

message: Hey fellow crutons!!! I have an announcement! If any of you are free the week of August 2nd through 7th the camp I will be working at needs more men to counsel! Otherwise they may have to turn down campers! :( so PLEASE consider helping out, or spread the word! Camp Cherith needs you!! If you have questions, you can ask me or check out the website!  Also, Megan Gullifer knows a little bit more about everything at camp too! (Sorry to volunteer you for info Sync, but I'm still learning stuff!) thanks guys! Have a great summer! http://camp-cherith.com
